title: Felon - S2E11 - Tara Costigan
description:
On average, at least one woman a week is killed by a partner or former partner in Australia…… 

If you or anyone you know has been or is a victim of domestic violence there are a number of hotlines you can call. 

https://www.whiteribbon.org.au/find-help/domestic-violence-hotlines/
http://www.taracostiganfoundation.com/
https://www.ourwatch.org.au/
